{"tid":1450381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<黑警還眼> 呢一刻問一問良心 佢地為你犧牲左幾多","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:34:21.000Z","uid":271050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"436e7cb2af85111c5d5e82a335930ca198b6067d","tid":1450381,"uid":271050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"同各位<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人</span>講個事實, <br />\n我地已經無得翻轉頭！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察同政府去到咁盡我地仲點忍？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係去擋子彈, 只係去<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">機場靜坐</span></span>！繼續和理非表達訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日1PM 罷工！百萬人塞爆機場！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「警察還眼」</span></span>五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n不衝禁區！不衝跑道！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">百萬人入機場！機場自然停！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/012508_6a1bb35959426601aae01fb9f9293b36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F012508_6a1bb35959426601aae01fb9f9293b36.png&h=1f406687&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6355e260406e5286e09d24d04470cd1dc3d3719","tid":1450381,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"2019年8月11日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}